{"tid":2026585,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滙豐總行員工餐廳變身大牌檔   採PayMe付款","createTime":"2020-05-21T05:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T05:36:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb3e77664ec426862ce86e068ce5aa4ab5720aa9","tid":2026585,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tSyO2pBqY9TRQuovahHSGw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjIwO2g9NDEz/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-05/10621280-9af1-11ea-bf7f-669b5c3ccb00\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtSyO2pBqY9TRQuovahHSGw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjIwO2g9NDEz%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-05%2F10621280-9af1-11ea-bf7f-669b5c3ccb00&h=341af434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滙豐中環總行地庫的員工餐廳幾個月前開始翻新，本月重開，裝修後格局類似大牌檔，除了繼續提供燒味飯和雙餸飯之外，更加入不少新選擇，包括港式小食，滙豐亞太區總裁王冬勝（Peter）鍾情的絲襪奶茶，滙豐一姐、香港區總裁施穎茵（Diana）最喜歡的雞蛋仔、印度脆薄餅及油雞髀飯都有供應，還有韓式炒年糕、藥材湯底的醉雞粉麵、墨西哥卷等，迎合不同文化地區的員工品味。<br />\n<br />\n餐廳的裝修除了改用大牌檔常用的大圓枱外，更仿照茶餐廳的復古瓷磚地板，以路牌為裝飾的特色牆，模仿巴士站的售票機，以及香港街景壁畫等，體現香港情懷。<br />\n<br />\n採PayMe付款<br />\n<br />\n凌通相信，不少滙豐員工都希望一試新餐廳食物。據悉，在目前抗疫大環境下，餐廳會遵守政府規定，座位之間作適當分隔，並鼓勵員工外賣。付款方面，當然會引入自家品牌的PayMe for Business。"},{"pid":"c8df9d4e7332740f89452c0c49d649bfaa49a605","tid":2026585,"uid":73565,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bb3e77664ec426862ce86e068ce5aa4ab5720aa9","tid":2026585,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tSyO2pBqY9TRQuovahHSGw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjIwO2g9NDEz/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-05/10621280-9af1-11ea-bf7f-669b5c3ccb00\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtSyO2pBqY9TRQuovahHSGw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9